response.original_title: Fillum Star: The Peter Patel Story
response.overview: Peter Patel (Rizwan Manji) is an Indian-American actor who becomes famous in his local community when they hear he is about to appear in a film alongside Tom Cruise. A documentary film crew follows him around for the two days leading up to the film's US premiere and witnesses the phenomenon of Peter's fame.
